{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2053558, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你说的这些都能顺利实现，那已经是很好很好的制度设计了", "timestamp": 1626102062, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是的，就是这样，本来就是一些很普通的事，不必过度拔高", "timestamp": 1626102197, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053577, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2053558, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 很好吗。。。被卷没的人呢，是代价吗", "timestamp": 1626102268, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053578, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就像里面说的一句话: 去基层好的话他们怎么不去", "timestamp": 1626102271, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得就是很真实的反映。没有为了刻意塑造什么。讲的故事都是真事，看上去并不假。也挺好（？）", "timestamp": 1626102289, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053594, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为了实现评职称，走仕途有很多比这些都便捷的手段，但是他们选择了能做实事的一条路，至少做实事也能使自己得到更多", "timestamp": 1626102396, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053602, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2053577, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我指的是让大家因为利益去做社会需要的事，并且能做好", "timestamp": 1626102461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2053594, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 基层选调的人多了去了，他们又不是真的一直在基层，只是签副处级，都需要去基层干两年，两年后回原职", "timestamp": 1626102495, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2053625, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", 