, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈哈这个嘛见仁见智喽。总不能宣传的时候就算这就是真实的清华对吧hhh。读出来什么看读者想要什么了。", "timestamp": 1626152252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2056864, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2056840, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 其实我觉得可以走接地气道路 平凡之中的坚定 这种宣传 没必要攀上理想（我看到还有很多类似的“看这部电影让你重拾大学的理想与热血”这样的宣传词", "timestamp": 1626152388, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2058331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "虽然但是，严同学并不是卷王（", "timestamp": 1626164549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2060280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2058331, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: qs", "timestamp": 1626182379, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2060284, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2058331, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 我看他最后进了一个很厉害的项目组，中间还有讲题，感觉很牛的样子", "timestamp": 1626182418, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2062465, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2055665, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 天底下哪有这么理想的事情，拉关系走后门，拉帮结派的多了去了，我持悲观态度。但我自己肯定不会去做，也没有机会去做“德不配位”的事。", "timestamp": 1626198587, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2873610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 400698, "reply_to": 2058331, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 为啥不用卷王", "timestamp": 1636199142, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 13, "pid": 400698, "reply": 31, "tag": null, "text": "是我太俗了吗，看《大学》觉得去基层就是为了仕途考虑，搞望远镜就是为了评职称，钱老师么，那一辈的精神早就没有了。至于严同学， 基本就是thu卷王的正常路数", "timestamp": 1626101905, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636199142, "url": "", "vote": {}}}